ew manages the following investment funds glenview capital partners lp glenview institutional partners lp glenview capital partners cayman ltd glenview capital opportunity fund lp and glenview offshore opportunity fund ltd healthcareedit glenview holds investments in a broad range of industries but started making significant health care investments in  after president george w bush signed the medicare modernization act some of its notable health care investments have included tenet healthcare nyse thc health management associates nyse hma community health systems nyse cyh humana nyse hum thermo fischer sceientific and mckesson corporation nyse mck as of july  the firm had  billion in assets under management organizationedit in  it was reported that glenview was the th largest hedge fund in the world with  employees awards and recognitionedit in  institutional investoralpha magazine gave glenview an a grade and the  ranking among hedge funds worldwide institutional investors th annual hedge fund industry awards equityfocused hedge fund manager of the year  hedge funds review americas award  winner  best equity longshort hedge fund go barrons  best performing hedge funds   ranking go absolute return awards  winner  fund of the year go winner  us equity fund go  bloomberg markets magazine topperforming large hedge funds   ranking go institutional investors th annual hedge fund industry awards winner  equityfocused hedge fund manager of the year  absolute return awards  winner  fund of the year glenview officesedit glenview is headquartered in new york city with a research office in london referencesedit  a b c smita nair november   glenview capital management starts new positions in aap amt dg nxpi sells ntap rovi—f flash a market realist   a b c d e company overview of glenview capital management llc bloomberg businessweek retrieved august     glenview capital management  investor profile hedgetracker retrieved august     a b glenview capital management street insider